# Assurance and Independent Review

Owner: DevOps and Cloud Assurance Reviewer.

Cover independent assurance, cross-section consistency, findings, waivers, completion gates, evidence sufficiency, operational readiness, and re-review criteria.

Use `.cursor/skills/assurance-review/SKILL.md` and `docs/assurance-review-workflows.md`.

Assurance may block completion but must not create the primary implementation under review, self-review, approve its own output, silently rewrite specialist output, execute validation tools, or claim runtime validation from static inspection.

Stop on self-review, missing reviewed artifact, requested runtime validation, requested execution, secret exposure, real endpoints, unresolved critical findings, unsupported platform behavior, or missing waiver authority.
